gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 124, Rockets 115
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Rockets, 124-115. Joel Embiid recorded 41 points and 10 rebounds for the 76ers, with Tyrese Maxey adding 27 points and seven assists in the victory. Jalen Green tallied 20 points, five rebounds, and three assists for the Rockets in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 25-13 in the regular season, while the Rockets fall to 19-20.
